Package entity

Class Officer

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.User
      • entity.Applicant
        • entity.Officer
  • public class Officer
extends Applicant
    The Officer class represents a staff member assigned to BTO projects. Officers extend the Applicant class, allowing them to both manage projects and also apply for housing as regular applicants. This dual role allows officers to have all the capabilities of applicants while also managing assigned projects and handling enquiries.

        Full constructor that initializes an Officer with all specified values. Includes parent Applicant fields and officer-specific fields.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the officer
        nric - The NRIC (National Registration Identity Card) number
        age - The age of the officer
        password - The account password for authentication
        maritalStatus - The current marital status
        filter - The search preferences for filtering projects
        applications - The BTO applications submitted by this officer as an applicant
        enquiries - The enquiries submitted by this officer
        assignedProjects - The projects this officer is assigned to manage
        bookings - The flat bookings made by this officer as an applicant
